            PonjoPastes has its own REST API that allows developers to interact with the website.
        </p>
        <ul class="text-white">
            <li>
                Create new pastes & fetch existing ones.
            </li>
            <li>
                The base URL for the API is <strong><a class="ponjo-link" href="https://pastes.ponjo.club/api/v1">https://pastes.ponjo.club/api/v1</a></strong>.
